msgctxt ""
"06070000.xhp\n"
"par_id31692405388098\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <menuitem>Format - Lists - Demote Outline Level with Subpoints</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຮູບແບບ - ລາຍການ - ຫຼຸດລະດັບໂຄງຮ່າງພ້ອມຈຸດຍ່ອຍ</menuitem>."

#. BzDr8
